    <item>
      <title>英国高昂的住房成本意味着成年子女在家居住的时间更长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/uk-s-high-housing-costs-mean-adult-children-live-at-home-longer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高昂的住房、儿童保育和学生债务成本，英国的年轻人比他们的前辈要花几年的时间才能达到人生的里程碑，包括离开父母的家和生孩子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/uk-s-high-housing-costs-mean-adult-children-live-at-home-longer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:31:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电获得 116 亿美元美国工厂补助和贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-08/tsmc-gets-11-6-billion-in-us-factory-grants-loans-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将向台积电提供 66 亿美元的赠款和高达 50 亿美元的贷款，帮助这家全球顶级芯片制造商在亚利桑那州建厂。埃德温·陈 (Edwin Chan) 接受彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-08/tsmc-gets-11-6-billion-in-us-factory-grants-loans-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波士顿考虑提高商业税以应对写字楼市场低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/boston-mulls-commercial-tax-hike-to-counter-office-market-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长吴米歇尔正在寻求提高商业地产税率，以帮助保护房主免受写字楼房产价值历史性暴跌的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/boston-mulls-commercial-tax-hike-to-counter-office-market-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
