    <item>
      <title>开始新的一天需要了解的五件事：美洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-08/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早上好。美国股指期货在周五强劲收盘后表现平淡，而随着交易员减少今年降息的押注，美国国债下跌。随着金价攀升至新纪录，油价从五个月高位回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-08/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:48:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着油价上涨，俄罗斯第一季度收入大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/russia-s-revenue-jumps-in-first-quarter-amid-rising-oil-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯报告第一季度收入大幅增长，部分原因是一次性纳税和油价上涨，因为该国继续承受因乌克兰战争而受到的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/russia-s-revenue-jumps-in-first-quarter-amid-rising-oil-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
